[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "ロロナ特製パイが焼けたよー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_018_038_00194",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ロロナ先輩のパイ……\n本当にごちそうになっていいんですか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00195",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "うん！　たくさん食べてくださいね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_018_038_00196",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ありがとう、ロロナちゃん！\nさ、果ての大陸への出航前に、景気づけね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00197",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ/レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "いただきます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00198_2",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "いただきます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00199",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "っん～～！！　いつも通り、とっても美味しいです！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00200",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "みんながアタシたちのために用意してくれたんだよね！\nたくさん食べて、航海のための体力をつけなくちゃ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00201",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "先輩方……ありがとうございます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00202",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "果ての大陸でマナを見つけて……そうすれば\n先輩方も元の世界に帰れる日が来ると思います",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00203",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "今まで異邦人の先輩方には多大なるご迷惑を\nおかけしていましたが、ようやく……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00204",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "迷惑になんて思ったことないですよ。ね、皆さん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_164_038_00205",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ライザ",
		"romanized_name": "Ryza",
		"model_path_hash": "244908326386260133",
		"text": "うんうん！　あたしだってそうだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_039_038_00206",
		"still_path_hash": "7897232981577117306",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "私たちにできることであれば、\n最後までお手伝いさせてください",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_164_038_00207",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "マリー",
		"romanized_name": "Marie",
		"model_path_hash": "1543991191416950894",
		"text": "頑張るわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_009_038_00208",
		"still_path_hash": "1729358731240541415",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "フィリス",
		"romanized_name": "Firis",
		"model_path_hash": "872339722236451917",
		"text": "おーっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_036_038_00209",
		"still_path_hash": "1330857698433587221",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ありがとうございます！　そう仰っていただけるのは\n幸甚の至りに存じます。ですが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00210",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "それこそ先輩方の助力のおかげで、\n元錬金党の皆さん、アルビーナ、リアスちゃん――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00211",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "この世界の錬金術士もたくさん頭角を現しています。\n自分たちの力で羽ばたく時が、ついに来たのかな、と！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00212",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ライザ",
		"romanized_name": "Ryza",
		"model_path_hash": "244908326386260133",
		"text": "……そっか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_039_038_00213",
		"still_path_hash": "7897232981577117306",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "分かりました。レスナさんがそう言うなら、\nその気持ち、大事にしないとですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_164_038_00214",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "パルメ族の二人にも、今度しっかり宣言するつもり\nです。いつまでも先輩方にご迷惑をかけないように",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00215",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "迷惑じゃないですよ……って、\nこれ、さっきも言いましたね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_164_038_00216",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "……でも、そっか。いよいよお別れの日も近いんだね。\nせっかく、みんなと仲良くなれたのに……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00217",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "分かってはいるけど、寂しいよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00218",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ライザ",
		"romanized_name": "Ryza",
		"model_path_hash": "244908326386260133",
		"text": "もー！　そんな寂しそうな顔しない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_039_038_00219",
		"still_path_hash": "7897232981577117306",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そんな暗い顔してたら、せっかくのパイも\n美味しくなくなっちゃうわよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00220",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "果ての大陸まで、私たちもお供します。\nその先のことは、終わってから考えましょうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_164_038_00221",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "そうだね！　まずはみんなで力を合わせて、\n果ての大陸へ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00222",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん！　先輩方、あと少しだけ、お力お借りします！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00223",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]